<section class='container'>
  <h2 class='section-title'>Target applications</h2>
  <div class='grid-3'>
    <div class='card'><h3>NF membrane screening</h3><p>Rapid comparative evaluation of membrane behaviour under centrifugal pressure conditions.</p></div>
    <div class='card'><h3>RO-oriented feasibility studies</h3><p>Compact experimental workflows for early stage assessment and ranking.</p></div>
    <div class='card'><h3>Rotor-native method development</h3><p>Screening campaigns designed around existing centrifuge infrastructure.</p></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class='container'>
  <div class='banner'>
    <h3>Application discussions should remain grounded.</h3>
    <p>Use phrases such as “designed for”, “optimized for”, “validated in” and “compatible with” rather than exaggerated superiority claims.</p>
  </div>
</section>

